EnExplanation: A change refers to the process of becoming different or undergoing a transformation in some way.

Samples.EeSentence: Ilm on pärast vihma muutunud soojemaks.
Samples.EnSentence: The weather has become warmer after the rain.

Samples.EeSentence: Ilm on teinud suure muutuse ja nüüd sajab lund.
Samples.EnSentence: The weather has made a big change and now it is snowing.
